{"tid":2452991,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[左翼集體失蹤]康奈爾香港學生單打獨鬥近兩年 堅持校園貼文宣、自製連儂橋","createTime":"2021-03-19T07:30:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T14:01:23.000Z","uid":210140,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e375deda121e85077787fdd340d25f5cb8c013e3","tid":2452991,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:30:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210319/LGWLX6RNIZFRDLGIRKBTOKL4LI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3AmrYI6yBhT3XqG7jkzk8WKwC75qdqqZvbssTru7mGe7SyPDp6BAd3BtE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210319%2FLGWLX6RNIZFRDLGIRKBTOKL4LI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3AmrYI6yBhT3XqG7jkzk8WKwC75qdqqZvbssTru7mGe7SyPDp6BAd3BtE&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=5ca4a4dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210319%2FLGWLX6RNIZFRDLGIRKBTOKL4LI%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3AmrYI6yBhT3XqG7jkzk8WKwC75qdqqZvbssTru7mGe7SyPDp6BAd3BtE&h=6e08d747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210319/LGWLX6RNIZFRDLGIRKBTOKL4LI/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3AmrYI6yBhT3XqG7jkzk8WKwC75qdqqZvbssTru7mGe7SyPDp6BAd3BtE</a><br />\n<br />\n（北美通訊）美國名校康奈爾大學（Cornell University）一名香港留學生，過去兩年一直「單打獨鬥」，堅持在校園四處張貼聲援香港民主運動的文宣，甚至自製「連儂橋」，但一直遭校內「小粉紅」中國學生撕毀。他向《蘋果》表示不會屈服，「他們一直撕，我便一直貼，比拼誰較有恆心。」<br />\n<br />\n在香港土生土長的高先生，自認是「和理非」。在2019年春夏之間，多次在港參與和平示威和集會「反送中」，也理解勇武抗爭的行為，堅持「不割蓆」。同年8月，他前往紐約康奈爾大學升學，當時香港的抗爭運動仍然如火如荼，令他非常掛心，於是9月起在校園內不同地方張貼文宣，更自製了一條貼滿告示貼的「連儂橋」，講解香港抗爭運動。<br />\n<br />\n高先生的努力很快招惹到「小粉紅」反擊，他表示，「連儂橋」告示貼通常在一晚、甚至幾小時內被撕毀；其他分散於校園不同角落的文宣，未必即時被人發現，但最終也會被撕毀，多數只保存數日至數星期。他說，一直未能確認撕毀文宣的人，但指出大學所在的綺色佳（Ithaca） 人口僅三萬人，因此很可能是校內中國政府支持者所為，旨在要他噤聲。<br />\n<br />\n到2019年11月，由於破壞文宣行為變本加厲，開始有人用噴漆弄髒公眾地方，高先生要求學生會（Student Assembly）代表全體本科生，譴責有關破壞行為。雖然學生會最終沒有通過譴責決議，但高先生在校內找到「同路人」，並獲邀加入學生組織「提倡東亞自由學會」（Society for the Promotion of East Asian Liberty，簡稱SPEAR），擔任學會聯席主席。<br />\n<br />\n目前，高先生已堅持在校園張貼撐港文宣一年半，他指，在去年9月至12月期間，由於大部份中國同學沒有返回紐約校園上課，文宣被撕的情況一度大幅減少；但很多中國留學生本學期回到校園，文宣被撕毀的數量又再增加。在兩、三周前，更有人疑似用打火機燒文宣，但他表明不會就此屈服。<br />\n<br />\n高先生認為，並非所有中國留學生皆是「小粉紅」， 他認識一些中國同學，對香港抗爭、爭取民主自由的心表示理解，但願意表態支持的人，始終是極少數，「無可否認小粉紅有很多，一名撐我的同學加入了中國同學的通訊群組，他告訴我，組內的人經常會提起我、駡我。」<br />\n<br />\n香港正式落實國安法後，大舉搜捕異見人士。高先生相信自己一旦回港，很大機會被捕，也擔心連累在香港的家人，但表示自己不會因此噤聲，「我始終有一個優勢，可以來到美國，就讀於一間頗有名的大學，我便覺得有責任為香港發聲。」"},{"pid":"da6d866b303d3f42b5e5578ee34df95b2d51363b","tid":2452991,"uid":251732,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"我真係好奇點解白左對支那人嘅所作所為不作聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006dc670f2db6ed9f4214436437dbf13638517ba","tid":2452991,"uid":210140,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"da6d866b303d3f42b5e5578ee34df95b2d51363b","tid":2452991,"uid":251732,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"我真係好奇點解白左對支那人嘅所作所為不作聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:35:19.000Z","msg":"左翼咪就係共產黨既黨羽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3970225caf7309484627ad650ccbebb8d0487497","tid":2452991,"uid":50931,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"da6d866b303d3f42b5e5578ee34df95b2d51363b","tid":2452991,"uid":251732,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"我真係好奇點解白左對支那人嘅所作所為不作聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:38:08.000Z","msg":"白左：香港人歧視支那人搞獨立係極右嘛"},{"pid":"2846172bb0a684400d2402529234321695678aa3","tid":2452991,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ab38d443e79e4235240289d599f3aba4ac4ca1","tid":2452991,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb2bb33e81b1f5dfad2ea21724a0273087a09f9c","tid":2452991,"uid":273723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:43:01.000Z","msg":"好有恆心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d149dc071edf889dc0b581a9fc7540007ced1c","tid":2452991,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:44:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d1e110b9b0fd61ae3d985f0306a952a6b0099e4","tid":2452991,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:46:53.000Z","msg":"撕紙係咪唔環保"},{"pid":"7b00dd2a8b6d0055c579fbbcbda69654c6cb8e19","tid":2452991,"uid":273723,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T07:50:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高先生相信自己一旦回港，很大機會被捕</blockquote><br />\n所以請你唔好返黎送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e628e4ecf74f64ae72f0eac354a9d5dd8b11d56a","tid":2452991,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}